Type of Feat: Item Creation
Prerequisite: Spellcaster Level  12th+.
Specifics: You can create a staff of any spell of 9th level or less that you know. To create a staff, cast an appropriate spell on a bone staff in your inventory. Creating a staff costs gold pieces based on the relative power of the spell. Staves containing first level spells can cost a few thousand gold pieces while those made with higher level spells can cost tens of thousands. Warlock invocations cannot be used in the creation of staves. Newly crafted staves have 50 charges.
Use: Cast a spell on a bone staff in your inventory.